Day 2 (Provisioning and securing a Windows Server VM)
•	Created an Azure Windows Server VM.
•	Implemented network-level controls using an Azure Network Security Group (NSG) to restrict RDP to my management IP.
•	Hardened the VM’s Windows Firewall and RDP settings.
•	Successfully connected via RDP (using restricted NSG rule).
